Description: Up for sale is a beautiful American Vintage 59 Stratocaster in three color burst. The fingerboard is a nice grainy piece of rosewood. The body is very clean except for a few chips by the neck plate and couple of very small chips on the body that I've tried to show in the pics. Includes all the cast candy. The pickguard has been replaced with a black pickguard giving it an SRV vibe. The case is not original case that came with the guitar (It is same model case but in black tolex instead of brown tolex) I. Save big over new prices where these are selling for $1900.00 - $2100.00. Please ask question before biding. No international shipping.
